<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Hogfather, let me ask a few final questions: Do you think it is fair that you can suddenly (after investing one hour of your time for a parchment) are able to wield the same power as a monk like Walkabout for example who invested a LOT of more of his time to enter VT etc? Do you REALLY believe this is what caster balance means?<br>
<br>
And please tell me where i said to nerf anything. If you read carefully i proposed some changes which i believe who will be good for the game. If i did not mention any other classes then it is because i do not know other classes well enough to say what will be good for them.<br>
